text: I've been along for the ride for the last 5-6 years, it's been amazing. I actually have a weird thing I do with this channel, randomly click on any video, or choose one, and when the song plays I think back to when I first played that particular game, or heard that song, and I just reminisce about the old days. Also if the video is older, I look at the upload date, and think about where I was in life at that time. It's a fun way to "relive" the past, and also realize how fast life can go by.
